  <brief_title>8-Week Study of Tolvaptan Dose Forms in Autosomal Dominant Polycystic Kidney Disease (ADPKD)</brief_title>
  <acronym>NOCTURNE</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Multicenter, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Double-blind, Placebo-masked, Parallel-group Pilot Trial to Compare the Efficacy, Tolerability, and Safety of Tolvaptan Modified-release and Immediate-release Formulations in Subjects With Autosomal Dominant Polycystic Kidney Disease</official_title>
